    <h1> Governance </h1>
    <p> The SUN CSN is governed by a steering group, under the leadership of a chair and vice chair. The day-to-day work of the network is coordinated by the SUN CSN secretariat, currently hosted by Save the Children UK. </p>
    <center>
    <%=image_tag("governance.jpg", alt: "Governance Structure of SUN CSN", title: "Governance Structure of SUN CSN")%>
